{"tid":1704171,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺橢圓運轉機好傷膝頭？","createTime":"2019-11-10T14:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T16:32:04.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c980eacd2d17da1f36c8ac1d417643c72eb3481b","tid":1704171,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"橢圓運轉機即係呢部野（下圖）<br />\n係GYM 房好常見 <br />\n類似跑步練Cardio 既器械 <br />\n但我成日都練到膝頭哥痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （p.s. 有加負重，心跳達80%，持續做60mins) <br />\n我跑步60mins 又唔見我膝頭哥痛 <br />\n反而用橢圓機練會痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我懷疑呢部機其實好傷膝頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fitnessconcept.com.hk/images/proTURE/PS900e_front.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fitnessconcept.com.hk%2Fimages%2FproTURE%2FPS900e_front.JPG&h=fd3a68d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3791a1e62cd345324b2c271b17ddc8a98736fc05","tid":1704171,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bfeb0646aca931decffbbe22874779cea51cf9","tid":1704171,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"試下唔用腳做"},{"pid":"f42f9a731f61f21d978626572b3bdf86e7670420","tid":1704171,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"我用30mins<br />\n男 level13-15 但跑得超慢 係咪我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid